questions, which drives her crazy.

18:00.064 --> 18:01.940
You're lucky you're cute.

18:02.770 --> 18:05.406
Oh, wait!

18:05.663 --> 18:07.566
I can't go to the movies.

18:07.799 --> 18:10.395
Where is my head?

18:10.500 --> 18:12.000
Oh, there it is!

18:15.284 --> 18:18.861
Anyhoo, uh, the thing is,
I totally promised my mom

18:18.961 --> 18:22.773
that I would help her...
make bolognese sauce.

18:22.876 --> 18:23.894
It's really
labor-intensive,

18:24.009 --> 18:26.502
but don't ask her about it,
because she won't remember.

18:26.613 --> 18:27.699
She's old.

18:27.971 --> 18:31.618
So have fun, you two!

18:32.028 --> 18:33.677
Go! Go!

18:34.480 --> 18:35.763
Okay, so, yeah.
The story is...

18:36.661 --> 18:38.705
Oh, hey, Sue,

18:38.873 --> 18:40.489
what did you want to
talk to me about?

18:40.794 --> 18:42.472
Oh, nothing.

18:42.767 --> 18:45.527
Uh, it was just
about the air conditioner

18:45.981 --> 18:49.977
and how it's broken
and can never be fixed.

18:50.576 --> 18:53.350
But we waited too long
to fix it,

18:53.978 --> 18:56.131
so I guess that's our fault.

18:56.236 --> 18:59.463
Well, regular air-conditioning
maintenance is important.

19:03.275 --> 19:05.416
It really is.

