the remote on top of the TV?

19:25.039 --> 19:26.546
You don't know
how I watch games.

19:26.699 --> 19:28.118
Oh, I know plenty.

19:28.373 --> 19:29.785
And you know what I think?

19:30.288 --> 19:31.897
I think you miss your son.

19:32.093 --> 19:33.082
Stop it.

19:33.186 --> 19:34.631
No, you do.

19:34.813 --> 19:37.483
You've got your phone in your
hand so you can keep checking it

19:37.590 --> 19:40.322
